backend/
├── model/           ← Business logic and data structures (Flashcard, Task, etc.)
│  
│
├── dsa/             ← DSA implementations (Trie, Sorting, Searching, etc.)
│  
│
├── database/        ← File handling / simple DB logic (CSV, JSON, etc.)
│   
│
└── BackendMain.java ← (Optional) test/demo backend functionality

frontend/
├── controller/              ← JavaFX controllers (handle user interaction)
│   
│
├── view/                    ← FXML files for each screen
│   
│
├── component/               ← Optional: reusable UI components
│   
│
├── style/                   ← CSS files for styling
│   
│
└── FrontendMain.java        ← JavaFX entry point
